@FOIAPost: not an issue in a normal year.
And that's it. (Asking about timeliness of annual FOIA reports after the shutdown was not a productive line of questioning, in terms of where problems with #opengov are right now.) #SunshineWeek

Now it's @RepAOC. Do you agree important for all of us to have compliance with FOIA? @FOIAPost: of course.
